        <heading>856.  Same; fraud, mistake, or condition of the mind</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 856.  Same; fraud, mistake, or condition of the mind
In pleading fraud or mistake, the circumstances constituting fraud or mistake shall be alleged with particularity.  Malice, intent, knowledge, and other condition of mind of a person may be alleged generally.</p>
        </content>
